      <item>
        <title>Batch rename files with the shell</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;A short script this week to replace spaces in filenames in a given folder.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Spaces will be replaced by underscores &lt;code&gt;_&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot; data-lang=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# Looping over files,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# forging new filename&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# and then renaming it.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for &lt;/span&gt;oldname &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do 
  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;newname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$oldname&lt;/span&gt; | sed -e &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/ /_/g&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt; 
  mv &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$oldname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$newname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This one remove the spaces, only the sed expression is different:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot; data-lang=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for &lt;/span&gt;oldname &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do 
  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;newname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$oldname&lt;/span&gt; | sed -e &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/ //g&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt; 
  mv &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$oldname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$newname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And this one lowercase all letters in addition to removing spaces:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot; data-lang=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for &lt;/span&gt;oldname &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do 
  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;newname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$oldname&lt;/span&gt; | sed -e &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/ //g&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;[:upper:]&#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;[:lower:]&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt; 
  mv &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$oldname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$newname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; This script is not recursive and will not rename files inside sub-directories.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
